(38, 1, '2014-01-21 17:25:13', '2014-01-21 17:25:13', '<!--:en--><p>This section of the website is intended at putting together the work done by the separate projects and wrapping up useful information that the partners could build on. This section gives a practical overview of the work done also with the assistance of Component-II and more specifically the events and materials being produced under Component-II. These would include the Sharing Seminars, Research, Cross field visits, Discussion forums. Since these are activities being organized and implemented by Component-II the materials to be uploaded in this section would be produced and delivered by Component-II. In that if information is necessary from the Component-I partners it shall be collected by the Component-II  team at ad hoc basis.  </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The initial creation of this section of the website was also discussed with UNIQUE II on previous occasions. Initially it was planned that the section would accommodate views/articles related with SAHRE programme and NFPE of Bangladesh. As such materials could also be uploaded in the “Knowledge” section or in the “Best practices” section the proposed restructuring of the “Learning from each other” could be discussed further with the partners.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As part of this section it is intended that a connection with the section “Discussion forums” shall be made. The Discussion forums are intended as a platform that would give an opportunity to the partners and interested counterparts to discuss any of the themes already reviewed by the Research papers, seminars, cross field visits, etc. The Component-I partners might be involved in the moderation of this discussions depending on their interest in the given theme.</p>\r\n<!--:-->', '<!--:en-->Learning from Each Other<!--:--><!--:bn-->একে অপরের থেকে শেখা<!--:-->', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'learning-from-each-other', '', '', '2014-01-30 20:42:04', '2014-01-30 20:42:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sharee