(282, 1, '2014-02-02 19:40:13', '2014-02-02 19:40:13', '<!--:en--><h1 style=\"color:blue; font-weight:bold;\">1st & 2nd Sharing Seminar </h1>\n<h3 style=\"color:blue; font-weight:bold;\">Dinajpur and Savar; November 2012</h3>\n\n<h3 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Sharing Seminar objectives</h3>\n\nThe seminars’ objectives were:\n•	to bring together key operatives from all four programmes;\n•	to discuss openly issues to do with working with the hardest to reach children;\n•	for participants to learn by sharing experience and expertise by working together;\n•	to gather information and examples of good practice, areas for further investigation etc. for review and dissemination;\n•	to collect recommendations from field operatives to NGOs and Government.\n\n\n\n\n<h3 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Expected outcomes </h3>\n\nThe expected outcomes of the seminar were:\n•	greater understanding of SHARE and the work of SHARE partners by implementers of the programme;\n•	greater communication between those implementers, possibly leading to on-going communication;\n•	reflection on their work, by seeing it in relation to that of others, possibly leading to new ideas and practices;\n•	examples of good practice collected for dissemination to other key operatives in NFE;\n\n<h3 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Perceived achievement of the expected outcomes in both seminars  </h3>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.sajibbiswas.com/shareeducation/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/www.png\"><img src=\"http://www.sajibbiswas.com/shareeducation/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/www.png\" alt=\"www\" width=\"598\" height=\"920\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-314\" /></a>\n\n\n<a href=\"<?php the_field(\'file_upload_knowledge\'); ?>\" class=\"more\" >Download File</a><!--:--><!--:bn-->ত্বে আ ফ ম রুহুল হক থাকার সময় এর অধিকাংশকে দলীয় বিবেচনায় অনুমোদন দেয়া হয় বলে অভিযোগ রয়েছে।স্বাস্থ্যমন্ত্রীর দায়িত্বে আ ফ ম রুহুল হক থাকার সময় এর অধিকাংশকে দলীয় বিবেচনায় অনুমোদন দেয়া হয় বলে অভিযোগ রয়েছে।স্বাস্থ্যমন্ত্রীর দায়িত্বে আ ফ 