(326, 1, '2014-02-03 05:06:53', '2014-02-03 05:06:53', '<!--:en-->The purpose of this section of the web site is to share materials developed and/or used by the implementing partners of Component-I of SHARE programme. This section acts as a resource bank of the materials produced by the SHARE programme and includes several sub-sections, that are grouped not by project (Aloghar, SHIKONII, etc.) but as type of material and intended target groups. Thus, the Programme is presented as one whole. The main objective of this section is to allow users to review what the partners’ projects have produced and are using in their work in Bangladesh. As such, regular uploading of materials in this section is vital. The partners can update Component-II with related documents on ad-hoc basis. As a minimum, they can present new materials at the time of delivery of the interim reports, when such materials are endorsed to the EUD. It is of high importance that the partners have received prior approval from the EUD.<!--:--><!--:bn-->নলেজ সেন্টার<!--:-->', '<!--:en-->Knowledge  Centre<!--:--><!--:bn-->নলেজ সেন্টার<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-03 05:06:53', '2014-02-03 05:06:53', '', 26, 'http://www.sajibbiswas.com/shareeducation/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
