(398, 1, '2015-07-04 05:04:19', '2015-07-04 05:04:19', '<!--:en-->The purpose of this section of the web site is to share materials developed and/or used by the implementing partners of SHARE education program. This section acts as a resource bank of the materials and there are sub-sections, that are grouped not by project (Aloghar, SHIKHON-II, etc.) but as type of material and intended target groups. The main objective of this section is to allow users to review what the partners’ projects have produced and are using in their work in Bangladesh.\n\nThere are six sub-sections, these are-\n\n<strong>Student learning materials:</strong> Student textbooks, supplementary reading materials, educational games etc.\n\n<strong>Classroom management:</strong> Teacher guide or manuals, lesson plans, student profile, student assessment form etc.\n\n<strong>Monitoring &amp; supervision:</strong> Tools and resources for teacher and programme supervision and administration, e.g. supervision checklist, classroom observation checklist etc.\n\n<strong>Teacher training:</strong> Curriculum, guide, manual etc.\n\n<strong>Parenting programme:</strong> Guide, manual etc.\n\n<strong>Awareness raising: </strong>Brochure, leaflet, poster, video, audio etc.\n<div id=\"__if72ru4sdfsdfrkjahiuyi_once\" style=\"display: none;\"></div>\n<div id=\"__zsc_once\"></div>\n<div id=\"__hggasdgjhsagd_once\" style=\"display: none;\"></div><!--:-->', '<!--:en-->Knowledge  Centre<!--:--><!--:bn-->নলেজ সেন্টার<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-07-04 05:04:19', '2015-07-04 05:04:19', '', 26, 'http://demo.share-education.org/26-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
