(685, 1, '2015-06-22 07:49:38', '2015-06-22 07:49:38', '<!--:en--><strong>Welcome to the SHARE Education Program Website.</strong>\r\n\r\nThis site is primarily a resource for the SHARE (Supporting the Hardest to Reach through Basic Education) program partners. SHARE is one of the largest Non-Formal Primary Education Programs in Bangladesh.\r\n\r\nThis site provides school level data and knowledge products developed by four SHARE projects-Aloghar, SHIKHON-II, SUSTAIN &amp; UNIQUE-II.\r\n\r\nAn Education Management Information System (EMIS) has been developed and integrated in this site with the help from Bureau of Non-Formal Education under Ministry of Primary and Mass Education for creating an enabling environment for the decision makers and implementers to take new initiatives for hardest to reach children in Bangladesh.\r\n\r\nThis website will help NFE implementers to avoid duplication, select program implementation areas, appropriate materials for teacher training and student learning. Further information can be obtained by contacting any of the four projects of SHARE education program or SHARE TA project (see contact tab).\r\n\r\nThis site is open and you do not need to be a member to access any part of it or to subscribe to any of the services provided.\r\n<div id=\"__if72ru4sdfsdfrkjahiuyi_once\" style=\"display: none;\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"__zsc_once\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"__hggasdgjhsagd_once\" style=\"display: none;\"></div><!--:-->', '<!--:en-->Overview<!--:--><!--:bn-->সাধারণভাবে 	<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-22 07:49:38', '2015-06-22 07:49:38', '', 40, 'http://share-education.org/40-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
