(1000, 1, '2017-09-20 03:10:20', '2017-09-20 03:10:20', 'During 2016 which was the last year of project implementation for SHIKHON II and penultimate year for the rest of the three projects was essentially a year to consolidate the gains and best practices, and complete the program on a high note. Three other projects continued their flurry of activities in all areas of their work. This annual report balances both the achievements of the program with the challenges faced; and provides a perspective that examines program activities both nationally and in specific regions of the country facing the greatest economic and educational challenges.', 'Annual Report 2016', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'annual-report-2016', '', '', '2017-09-20 03:10:20', '2017-09-20 03:10:20', '', 0, 'http://share-education.org/?post_type=knowledgecentre&#038;p=1000', 0, 'knowledgecentre', '', 0);
