(1006, 1, '2017-10-23 08:01:46', '2017-10-23 08:01:46', '<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 8\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\nThis toolkit presents a set of monitoring concepts, frameworks, data gathering, analysis and reporting tools to monitor and evaluate Non Formal Primary Education (NFPE) related program. Written primarily for the monitoring and evaluation related personnel in the four projects under the SHARE program (SUSTAIN, UNIQUE II, SHIKHON II and Aloghar), it constitutes a series of concepts, tools and techniques that are practical, useful and relevant to the SHARE program. This can also serve as a generic toolkit for the NFPE sub-sector in Bangladesh, if needed.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Monitoring and Evaluation (M&E) Toolkit', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'monitoring-and-evaluation-me-toolkit', '', '', '2017-10-23 08:01:46', '2017-10-23 08:01:46', '', 0, 'http://share-education.org/?post_type=knowledgecentre&#038;p=1006', 0, 'knowledgecentre', '', 0),
